2014-03-25 15:31:31	smrtz|nix	I need a connector to replace the one on the bullet though.  Can you guys help me find one?
2014-03-25 15:31:42	gordonjcp	why do you need to replace the connector on the bullet?
2014-03-25 15:31:44	smrtz|nix	gordonjcp: no, but I'm just trying to make an omni whip.
2014-03-25 15:31:52	gordonjcp	smrtz|nix: okay, that should be easy enough
2014-03-25 15:31:57	smrtz|nix	gordonjcp: it's much to heavy for us, we're mounting it in an RC airplane.
