2014-03-25 15:35:41	gordonjcp	(so, probably not a UK Foundation licence, for example)
2014-03-25 15:35:47	smrtz|nix	gordonjcp: no, it's for standard wifi, in a compotition where we're all given special allowance to use this stuff.
